DESCRIPTION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Test event to verify mutual exclusivity validation for COUNT and UNTIL.\nThis event has BOTH count and until parameters\, which violates RFC 5545.\nExpected behavior: Build should fail with error message about mutual exclusivity.\nError message should be: “RRULE cannot have both COUNT and UNTIL (RFC 5545 Section 3.3.10)”
LAST-MODIFIED:20260430T135516Z
LOCATION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Test Location
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY;LANGUAGE=en-US:Test COUNT and UNTIL Conflict
TRANSP:OPAQUE
URL:https://finkregh.github.io/hugo-theme-component-ical/pr-preview/pr-42/events/test_count_until_conflict/

RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;INTERVAL=1;COUNT=20;BYDAY=FR

DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME;TZID=Europe/Zurich:20260301T170000
CONTACT;LANGUAGE=en-US:Test Organizer: test@example.org
COLOR:crimson
END:VEVENT
